OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775567469
OL,3,CFather of Charlie Cosser calls for
OL,4,Cknife crime lessons for nine-year-olds
OL,6,FThe father of a teenager stabbed to
OL,7,Fdeath at a party in Sussex said
OL,8,Fchildren should be educated about
OL,9,Fknife crime in every school from the
OL,10,Fage of nine.
OL,12,FMartin Cosser lost his son Charlie,
OL,13,F17, after he was attacked during a
OL,14,Fnight out in Warnham. A fight broke
OL,15,Fout on the dancefloor and Charlie was
OL,16,Fstabbed repeatedly in the chest.
OL,18,FThe government said it wanted to
OL,19,Ftarget knife-crime hotspots with
OL,20,Fspecialist training in schools to
OL,21,Fdivert children away from criminality.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775567469
OL,3,CFather of Charlie Cosser calls for
OL,4,Cknife crime lessons for nine-year-olds
OL,6,FMartin Cosser said early intervention
OL,7,Fwas essential, adding: "I think if we
OL,8,Flook historically about how we tackle
OL,9,Fknife crime, we're very reactive.
OL,11,F"We need to start educating. We need
OL,12,Fthat early intervention and we need to
OL,13,Fbe dealing with that at a young age."
OL,15,FCharlie Cosser, from Milford in
OL,16,FSurrey, was described by his family as
OL,17,Fa calm, easy-going teenager who had
OL,18,Fjust started an apprenticeship and
OL,19,Fwanted to get a job as Head Groundsman
OL,20,Fat Chelsea Football Club.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775567469
OL,3,CFather of Charlie Cosser calls for
OL,4,Cknife crime lessons for nine-year-olds
OL,6,FYura Varybrus, who was 16 at the time
OL,7,Fof the killing, was convicted of
OL,8,FCharlie's murder and jailed for life
OL,9,Fwith a minimum term of 16 years.
OL,11,FCharlie's dad said he received
OL,12,Fhundreds of messages every week from
OL,13,Fparents and teachers - and also young
OL,14,Fpeople - about knife crime.
OL,16,FHe said there were "missed
OL,17,Fopportunities" to save lives, adding:
OL,18,F"I'd like to see education in every
OL,19,Fsingle school, in primary schools,
OL,20,Ffrom key stage two.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775567469
OL,3,CFather of Charlie Cosser calls for
OL,4,Cknife crime lessons for nine-year-olds
OL,6,F"We're talking about age nine. At that
OL,7,Fage, they are young, they're
OL,8,Finquisitive, they want to feel safe.
OL,10,F"They've got so many questions, and
OL,11,Fthat's when we need to be getting to
OL,12,Fthem. But before we do that, we need
OL,13,Fto upskill our teacher population.
OL,15,F"There is no point putting this on the
OL,16,Fcurriculum until we've done that.
OL,18,F"And if you look in mainstream
OL,19,Fschools, only 15% of teachers are
OL,20,Fconfident enough to talk about knife
OL,21,Fcrime.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775567469
OL,3,CFather of Charlie Cosser calls for
OL,4,Cknife crime lessons for nine-year-olds
OL,6,F"That needs to change."
OL,8,FThe government said a #1.2 million
OL,9,Finvestment was planned to provide
OL,10,Fspecialist training in up to 250
OL,11,Fschools in areas most affected by
OL,12,Fknife crime, with more intensive and
OL,13,Ftailored support provided to up to 50
OL,14,Fof these schools.
OL,16,FThis investment is intended to fund
OL,17,Fmeasures such as mentoring for high-
OL,18,Frisk students and the deployment of
OL,19,Fchaperones on school routes.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775567469
OL,3,CFather of Charlie Cosser calls for
OL,4,Cknife crime lessons for nine-year-olds
OL,6,FThe Safety In & Around Schools
OL,7,FPartnership will train school leaders
OL,8,Fon knife-crime risk and develop local
OL,9,Fsolutions to improve pupil safety and
OL,10,Fprevent serious violence.
OL,12,FSarah Jones, crime and policing
OL,13,Fminister, said: "No child should fear
OL,14,Fwalking to school. That is why we must
OL,15,Fprevent violence from ever occurring.
OL,17,F"With the right support, the right
OL,18,Fopportunities and the right
OL,19,Finterventions in the right places, we
OL,20,Fcan prevent harm long before a young
OL,21,Fperson finds themselves in danger."
OL,26,@uD@QOUyD@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/13
