OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775567469
OL,3,CFather of Charlie Cosser calls for
OL,4,Cknife crime lessons for nine-year-olds
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIt comes as the first wave of youth
OL,12,Fhubs aimed at giving young people
OL,13,Fsupport with jobs and wellbeing are
OL,14,Fset to open across England.
OL,16,FThe centres will help young people
OL,17,Faged up to 18 with employment advice,
OL,18,Fhealth and wellbeing, and are also
OL,19,Faimed at preventing them from falling
OL,20,Finto a life of crime.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775567469
OL,3,CFather of Charlie Cosser calls for
OL,4,Cknife crime lessons for nine-year-olds
OL,6,FAreas of high anti-social behaviour
OL,7,Fhave been targeted for the first wave
OL,8,Fof the hubs, but they will be among 50
OL,9,Fwhich will open across the country.
OL,11,FShadow home secretary Chris Philp
OL,12,Faccused Labour of having "a massive
OL,13,Fcheek" making its announcement while
OL,14,Fcutting total police numbers.
OL,26,@tD@ZOUuD@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
