OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775567469
OL,3,CFather of Charlie Cosser calls for
OL,4,Cknife crime lessons for nine-year-olds
OL,6,FHe said: "In London, they even
OL,7,Fscrapped dedicated police officers in
OL,8,Fschools completely ` and now they
OL,9,Fclaim to be worried about the
OL,10,Fresulting school crime. They created
OL,11,Fthis mess in the first place with
OL,12,Ftheir police cuts."
OL,14,FPledging that his party would "go
OL,15,Ffurther and be tougher", Mr Philp said
OL,16,Fthe Conservatives would have "zero
OL,17,Ftolerance" for violence or serious
OL,18,Fdisruption in schools.
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@SO]vD@_OUwD@WO]xD@^OUyD@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775567469
OL,3,CFather of Charlie Cosser calls for
OL,4,Cknife crime lessons for nine-year-olds
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat justice spokeswoman
OL,7,FJess Brown-Fuller said: "Too many
OL,8,Fyoung lives have been lost to knife
OL,9,Fcrime and schools have been crying out
OL,10,Ffor further support to tackle it, but
OL,11,Fthese measures alone won't be enough
OL,12,Fto end the plight.
OL,14,F"The Government needs to focus on
OL,15,Freturning to proper community policing
OL,16,Fwhere people know their local officer,
OL,17,Fand ensure that right across the
OL,18,Fcountry young people have access to
OL,19,Fyouth services."
OL,26,@oD@YOUvD@AOU{D@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
