OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775567469
OL,3,CFather of Charlie Cosser calls for
OL,4,Cknife crime lessons for nine-year-olds
OL,6,FMartin Cosser said when he was a child
OL,7,Fhe never felt unsafe leaving home but
OL,8,Furgent action was now needed to tackle
OL,9,Fviolent crime.
OL,11,F"The love of my son motivates me," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"Stopping other families from feeling
OL,15,Fas my family feels, living as my
OL,16,Ffamily lives, that's what inspires me.
OL,18,F"I have been motivated and inspired by
OL,19,Fyoung people since I've been doing
OL,20,Fthis work. We need to raise the voice
OL,21,Fof our young people.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775567469
OL,3,CFather of Charlie Cosser calls for
OL,4,Cknife crime lessons for nine-year-olds
OL,6,F"We need to make them feel valued and
OL,7,Fwe need to bring them along this
OL,8,Fjourney because they are our future.
OL,10,F"And when you talk to young people I
OL,11,Fbelieve generally now the gap between
OL,12,Fthe adult population and young people
OL,13,F- part of that is the evolution of
OL,14,Ftechnology - it's getting wider and
OL,15,Fwider and wider.
OL,17,F"We need to close it."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
